reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Affordable and Efficient, with a Slight Compromise on Longevity
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased this pack of CR2032 lithium batteries, and I've been pleasantly surprised by their performance, especially considering their great price point. One standout feature for me is their compatibility with AirTags. Unlike some other batteries, these don't have the bitterant coating, which often causes issues with AirTags. This makes them an ideal choice for anyone using these tracking devices.The batteries themselves work well and provide a reliable power source for my AirTags. It's a relief not to worry about the batteries causing malfunctions or being incompatible. This aspect alone has made my experience with these batteries quite satisfactory.However, there is a trade-off when it comes to battery life. I've noticed that these batteries tend to last about 70-80% as long as some of the more premium options available on the market. Once installed in my AirTags, I found myself needing to replace them a bit sooner than I would with higher-end batteries. This shorter lifespan is noticeable, but it's not a deal-breaker for me.Considering the affordability of these batteries, I still find them to be a worthwhile purchase. They strike a good balance between cost and functionality, especially for applications like AirTags where compatibility is key. While the slightly reduced longevity is a factor to keep in mind, the overall value and performance of these batteries make them a sensible choice for anyone looking for a cost-effective solution for their devices.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Five Stars for Lasting Power and Convenience: LiCB CR2032 Batteries Deliver!
reviews.reviewText: I'm always on the hunt for reliable batteries that won't leave me hanging, and the LiCB CR2032 10-pack has definitely become my go-to! These little powerhouses have been a game-changer for all my devices that use these button cell batteries.Long-lasting performance: Forget the days of constantly swapping out dead batteries. These LiCB CR2032s hold their charge for what feels like forever! My laser pointer, which used to be a battery hog, has been going strong for months now. My garage door opener, a notorious battery drainer, hasn't even hinted at needing a replacement yet.Bulk pack convenience: Let's be honest, no one wants to run out of these tiny batteries at an inconvenient time. Having a 10-pack on hand ensures I'm always prepared. Plus, the price per battery is fantastic when you buy them in bulk.No leaks, no worries: I've used some cheap button cell batteries in the past that have leaked and damaged my devices. Not these! The LiCB CR2032s seem to be built to last, and I haven't experienced any leaks or corrosion whatsoever.Versatile power: These batteries are the workhorses of the button cell world. From my watch and car key fob to my medical devices and even some of my kid's toys, the LiCB CR2032s have powered them all flawlessly.Overall, I couldn't be happier with these batteries. They're reliable, long-lasting, and convenient to have around. If you're looking for a high-quality button cell battery that won't let you down, I highly recommend the LiCB CR2032 10-pack. Five stars all the way!
